markdownRemark.html:
Good episode! Finally some training. However, it was way too easy. Way back when it used to take Naruto quite some episodes to get something. Like when he tried to learn the Rasengan it was a very long way.

Now, this dude has evolved his attack in just 1 day, c’mon.
